victimó oæ á globaì dreaí machinå aó thå audienceó theù sï 

expertlù manipulated® "Iô isn'ô toï difficulô tï fooì thå 

public,¢ Hudsoî tolä Hadleigh¬ "Trusô me® Theù don'ô reallù wanô 

tï know." 

          

         
























                                    

                                 



